<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - BMC estimate raised.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - BMC estimate raised.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-07-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>SoundView Financial said Thursday analyst Jim Mendelson raised his fiscal 1998 earnings estimate on BMC Software Inc.</p>
<p>-- Raised estimate to $2.06 per share from $1.95.</p>
<p>-- Set 1999 estimate at $2.44.</p>
<p>-- Kept short- and long-term ratings at buy.</p>
<p>-- BMC late Wednesday reported a first quarter loss of $0.10 per share versus a profit of $0.26 a year ago.</p>
<p>-- Shares fell 2-1/2 to 57-7/8.</p>
